	<div class="post post-96592 clearfix  category-uncategorized">
		<div class="slugs"><a title="100% true" href="http://thehairpin.com/slug/100-true">100% true</a></div>
		<a class="comments" href="http://thehairpin.com/2015/02/and-now-for-something-completely-normal#comments">1</a>

				<h2><a    title="And Now For Something Completely Normal" href="http://thehairpin.com/2015/02/and-now-for-something-completely-normal">And Now For Something Completely Normal</a></h2>
		<div class="byline">
			<a title="Definitely &quot;Haley&quot;" href="http://thehairpin.com/user/64881/definitely-haley">Definitely &quot;Haley&quot;</a>			<a class="time" href="http://thehairpin.com/2015/02/and-now-for-something-completely-normal">@ 10:30 am</a>
		</div>
		
		<div class="entry clearfix">
			<p><a href="http://thehairpin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Patrick-and-Keanus-Wacky-Funtime-Magic-Emporium.jpg"><img src="http://thehairpin.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/Patrick-and-Keanus-Wacky-Funtime-Magic-Emporium.jpg" alt="Patrick and Keanu&#039;s Wacky Funtime Magic Emporium" width="640" height="384" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-96594" /></a></p>

<p>Hello, it is I, Haley Bertha Mlotek, editor of esteemed website thehairpin.com. You might have heard some rumors that I was away this week filming <em>The Real World: Des Moines</em> but that is not true! I have been here all week, sitting at my desk in Canada, listening to the Drake and reading the World Wide Web. There is absolutely nothing out of the ordinary here.</p>

<p>I am here to announce some new changes that I, Haley Gertrude Mlotek, definitely and 100% sign off on:</p>

<p>1. The new tagline for The Hairpin will be “Jazmine and Anna’s Wacky Funtime Magic Emporium.” The new header image will be a photo of Jazmine and Anna exchanging enthusiastic high fives while wearing festive hats on their heads. A different set of hats will be depicted every week.</p>

<p>2. The third Thursday of every month will now be known as “Danny DeVito and Steve Buscemi Erotic Fan Fiction Day.” Submissions will be considered only if they contain Danny DeVito, Steve Buscemi, or Danny DeVito and Steve Buscemi together. Please send submissions to haley@thehairpin.com and be as graphic as possible. Accompanying fan art is encouraged, but not necessary.  <a class="more-link" title="Read More" href="http://thehairpin.com/2015/02/and-now-for-something-completely-normal#more">READ MORE</a></p>		</div><!-- .entry -->
	</div><!-- .post -->













