		<div class="byline">
			<a title="Anna Fitzpatrick" href="http://thehairpin.com/user/8681/anna-fitzpatrick">Anna Fitzpatrick</a>			<a class="time" href="http://thehairpin.com/2015/02/this-man-took-a-photo-of-his-wife-the-same-day-every-year-for-a-decade-you-wont-believe-the-results">| February 18, 2015</a>
